 </paragraph><paragraph id="H6506AD7E6C59445BB96DB96B543FD7DE"><enum>(2)</enum><text>The term <term>veteran</term> has the meaning given such term in section 101 of title 38, United States Code.</text></paragraph></subsection><after-quoted-block>.</after-quoted-block></quoted-block> </paragraph></section></legis-body></bill> 

